values:
my boithday has snuck up on me again.
I will be going to Ghoul Skool next week.
24.
I think I say this every year, but...I thought I'd be locked up in jail or an asylum or be 6 feet under right now. From the kinda shit I use to do back then I have no regrets to speak of. I wouldn't have done anything different.

I got to where I'm today by doing what I did. 
And I think I'm doing alright.

That's all.

I'm starting to miss mah old journal........how gay.

Should I go back?
Be strong; and Shout at the Lawn Gnomes!!!

I'm sitting here in mah room mixing a tape for Em. KISS, Quiet Riot, Motley Crue and what have you. Gonna post up a big blank piece of canvas on one wall. 9ft x 13ft.....Hmmmm. lotsa space. Also taking my mic stand and wiring a human skull to it along w/ numerous other bones I have acquired.

My back hurts a lot. Must remember when I'm bringing back 50 lbs of aluminum bar stock to my lathe; lift with legs. *nods*

My sister may be coming down for a week to visit and my brother may be going to Double Check(rehab) next week.

I, on the other hand, have become addicted to tying myself up and having someone toss a wolverine high on angel-dust into a steel box along w/ me.

I love my life.

I'm on my lunch. Work is extra frustrating today. Anyone ever try to chase a measurement?
No?
Well, Its the stupidest thing in the fucking world.
And there seems to be napalm in mah burrito
*smack*
I have a boner.
Lets do pills.

well well well....

I'm alive and feeling fan-fucking tastic. Here on my lunch. My room is fixed up better than ever. just a blue light in there. new desk. great roomates. girlfriend can spend the night over more often. She may be staying over for a few days while her hous is getting painted. all has been very VERY good.

going to bang this weekend for someething to do....

I may be on here less. To my close friends who call from across the states, e-mail me for phone # info.

Miss you all...back to my buffalo wings.

DAMN! Been awhile? Just got home from work. I got a shitload of work done today. I'm starting the residential shifting process tonight over to Dianne's. Right now I'm running around like a armless egglaying baby.

you ever wake up and feel the stringy parts of muscle pulling your tounge back down into your throat?

oh......me niether.

Well, I'm home from work. Can't really think of even one bad day working there. I wake up eager to get there and leave feeling acomplished. Found a quiet neighborhood to move into. Going to Camarillo.....I think, "How WHITE of me." is the correct thing to say. Life has been starting out on a whole new page this year.




....I still want to buttfuck a black vicerated midget....

A new begining...like a baby locust with wings still wet.

Welcome to my cranial vomit.
